-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n侵侵叫大陸還清朝債卷<br />\n大陸唔肯還都仲未知<br />\n佢話前朝,唔認佢要還<br />\n如果唔駛還,唔認,咁點解要還香港<br />\nbloomberg同台灣都有講, 點解香港無黎聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔還得起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n應該還俾承認的一個政權<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-29%2Ftrump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=5fc8f3cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=f2e878ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7RnZZ8.png&h=a10eff3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"654e37a175bd0288dd6ac41fffdc9240861f98c7","tid":1534892,"uid":256019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"等埋呢個零月，睇定係硬定軟脫歐先，如果係硬脫就隨時見8字頭..."},{"pid":"affd677336f4313c620af25ca42b127ec9477c2b","tid":1534892,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"654e37a175bd0288dd6ac41fffdc9240861f98c7","tid":1534892,"uid":256019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"等埋呢個零月，睇定係硬定軟脫歐先，如果係硬脫就隨時見8字頭..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:38:31.000Z","msg":"睇歐盟阻唔阻止硬脫，阻 = 止跌，唔阻 = 仲有得跌"},{"pid":"f5842457756a75359d6be24b9bb22d2cc434e435","tid":1534892,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":